**LCD filter** (in Fontconfig / FreeType) controls **how subpixel color components are blended**
when **subpixel antialiasing (RGB/BGR)** is used.
It reduces **color fringing** by smoothing how much each subpixel contributes.

Think of it as a **low-pass filter for RGB subpixels**.

